				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/rt-interview-anniversary-edward-snowden.html" title="16:58" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-06-10T16:58:30+00:00" pubdate>June 10, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
