	<article id="post-3732" class="post-3732 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-art-and-culture category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-intelligence category-privacy-2 category-spies category-surveillance category-tv category-whistleblowers tag-activism tag-art tag-civil-liberties-2 tag-european-media-art-festival tag-orwell tag-privacy tag-snowden tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/04/european-media-art-festival-emaf-osnabrueck.html" title="Permalink to European Media Art Festival (EMAF), Osnabrueck" rel="bookmark">European Media Art Festival (<span class="caps">EMAF</span>), Osnabrueck</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/04/european-media-art-festival-emaf-osnabrueck.html" title="22:22" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-04-23T22:22:58+00:00" pubdate>April 23, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/04/european-media-art-festival-emaf-osnabrueck.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>The 27<sup>th</sup> <a href="http://www.emaf.de/english/start.html">European Media Art Fest­ival</a> began this even­ing in Osnab­rueck, Ger­many. In the wake of all the global intel­li­gence whis­tleblow­ing that has gone on over the last few years, the theme for the artists of 2014 is “<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/03/alleged-wikileaks-source-bradley-manning-faces-the-death-penalty.html">We, the Enemy</a>”.</p>
<p>Do visit if you can — a lot of inter­est­ing and polit­ical art install­a­tions are on dis­play, as well as films, music, and talks.  I shall be doing a talk on speak­ing on Fri­day afternoon.</p>
<p>I had the pleas­ure of mak­ing a short speech at the open­ing cere­mony this even­ing, and did an inter­view for national Ger­man <span class="caps">TV</span> chan­nel <span class="caps">ARD</span> last night to pub­li­cise the festival.</p>
<p><img src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/ueberwachungskunst.jpg" alt="ueberwachungskunst" width="706" height="397" class="placeholder alignleft size-full wp-image-3817" data-source="vimeo" data-id="92751800" /></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/92751800">Uber­wachungs kunst</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
