						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/04/cia-chief-visits-ukraine-why.html" title="20:50" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-04-17T20:50:15+00:00" pubdate>April 17, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
