                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>My recent inter­view on <span class="caps">RT</span> about Ukraine and inter­ven­tion­ism, both West and East:</p>
<p><img src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/cia_ukraine.jpg" alt="cia_ukraine" width="709" height="397" class="placeholder alignleft size-full wp-image-3815" data-source="vimeo" data-id="92136052" /></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/92136052"><span class="caps">US</span> mis­cal­cu­lated will of Ukrain­ian people</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
