												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/accountability" title="View all posts in Accountability" rel="category tag">Accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/big-brother" title="View all posts in Big Brother" rel="category tag">Big Brother</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/machon" title="View all posts in Machon" rel="category tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/privacy-2" title="View all posts in Privacy" rel="category tag">Privacy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/snowden" title="View all posts in Snowden" rel="category tag">Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/surveillance" title="View all posts in Surveillance" rel="category tag">Surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/talks-2" title="View all posts in Talks" rel="category tag">Talks</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/war-2" title="View all posts in War" rel="category tag">War</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>			</span>
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/annie-machon" rel="tag">Annie Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/bill-binney" rel="tag">Bill Binney</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/chris-hedges" rel="tag">Chris Hedges</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/chris-huhne" rel="tag">Chris Huhne</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/debate" rel="tag">debate</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/democracy-2" rel="tag">democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/edward-snowden" rel="tag">Edward Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/oxford-union-society" rel="tag">Oxford Union Society</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>			</span>
						
