							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/chelsea-manning" rel="tag">Chelsea Manning</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/courage" rel="tag">Courage</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/courage-foundation" rel="tag">Courage Foundation</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/edward-snowden" rel="tag">Edward Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/eileen-chubb" rel="tag">Eileen Chubb</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gavin-macfadyen" rel="tag">Gavin MacFadyen</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/government-accountability-project" rel="tag">Government Accountability Project</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/jesselyn-radack" rel="tag">Jesselyn Radack</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/ray-mcgovern" rel="tag">Ray McGovern</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/saaii" rel="tag">SAAII</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/the-centre-for-investigative-journalism" rel="tag">the Centre for Investigative Journalism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/the-whistler" rel="tag">The Whistler</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/thomas-drake" rel="tag">Thomas Drake</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>			</span>
						
